channel.title: [Tut]Aryan Fix
channel.description:
Well i've seen countless of topics about "Omg my aryan doesnt work help pl0x" and all the problems are the same... People, learn to use the dam search button, either that or read
Now for the fix: [IMG]http://i3.photobucket.com/albums/y99/ShadowZScar/AccessorMethods.jpg[/img]
When you receive this error, you go to Aryan -> Botclasses -> AccessorMethods.java -> Search for [code]anInt950[/code] -> Make it [code]rs.anInt950[/code]
Get the javac is not reconized error ? Make sure you installed the required java you need, then follow this
http://img515.imageshack.us/img515/1562/untitled117yc3ma.gif - Credit goes to swift
Copy variables:
Path [code]C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin;C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.5.0_06\bin[/code]
Classpath [code]SET CLASSPATH=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin;%CLASSPATH%;.[/code]
Hope this brighten up stuff
